            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-1-hotel-brooklyn-bridge.png", alt: "1 Hotel Brooklyn Bridge"

            p Set in Brooklyn Bridge Park along the East River, this trendy hotel is designed with local artisans and reclaimed materials and is inspired by the Manhattan skyline views.

