        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
          .ContentCopy__partner
            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-pottery-barn.png", alt: "Pottery Barn"

            p Pottery Barn inspires customers to create homes that are comfortable, beautiful and true to their personal style. We offer timeless, high-quality furniture and decor in a variety of sizes and aesthetics, and provide fresh ideas that make the home-decorating process easy and rewarding. From the artists who design products in our San Francisco studios to the stylists and master craftspeople we employ around the world, we work every day to help others make their homes for life.

            p #{link_to "Visit Pottery Barn", "https://www.potterybarn.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}

        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
          .ContentCopy__partner
            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-morgan-lane.png", alt: "Morgan Lane"

            p Morgan Lane is a New York based lingerie, sleep and swimwear brand founded in 2014 by Morgan Curtis, one of 2016’s CFDA Vogue Fashion Fund Finalists. She is known for making lifestyle pieces that can be worn both as sleepwear and ready-to-wear. Her fun and effortless approach to luxury intimates is represented in each and every piece she creates.

            p #{link_to "Visit Morgan Lane", "https://www.morgan-lane.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}

      .row
        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
          .ContentCopy__partner
            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-williams-sonoma.png", alt: "Williams Sonoma"

            p Since its founding by Chuck Williams in 1956, the Williams Sonoma brand has been bringing people together around food. A member of Williams-Sonoma, Inc. portfolio of brands, Williams Sonoma is a leading specialty retailer of high-quality products for the kitchen and home, providing world-class service and an engaging customer experience.

