            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-eberjey.png", alt: "Eberjey"

            p Co-founded by Ali Mejia and Mariela Rovito in 1996, women’s lifestyle brand Eberjey creates soft, luxurious separates that encourage women to feel beautiful from the inside out. With comfort at its core, feminine, wearable pieces offer everyday beauty and versatility for women on-the-go. Sophisticated collections focus on forgiving silhouettes, suitable coverage and multi-functional styles that accentuate a woman’s inner strength and confidence.

            p #{link_to "Visit Eberjey", "https://www.eberjey.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}

      .row
        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
          .ContentCopy__partner
            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-tde.png", alt: "The Daily Edited"

            p The Daily Edited is an accessories company all about creating products where form meets function, a notion of understated chic, and the creation of products with a luxury feel at an attainable price point.

            p #{link_to "Visit TDE", "https://www.thedailyedited.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}

        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
