            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-nina-bridal.png", alt: "Nina Bridal"

            p Nina Footwear Corp., located in New York City since 1953, offers fashion footwear with an emphasis on glamour.  Nina dominates the market as the leading resource for evening and bridal shoes in the United States, offering women designer product and style at great value. Nina finely-crafted shoes, exquisite handbags, and heirloom quality jewelry are frequently featured on television, in top fashion magazines and on the red carpet.

            p #{link_to "Visit Nina Bridal", "https://ninashoes.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}

        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
          .ContentCopy__partner
            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-stylisted.png", alt: "Stylisted"

            p Stylisted allows women to book on-location hair styling and makeup appointments from freelance professionals. Skip the salon, select the professional for your needs, and wait for beauty to knock at your door.

            p #{link_to "Visit Stylisted", "https://stylisted.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}

      .row
        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
          .ContentCopy__partner
            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-blushington.png", alt: "Blushington"

            p Blushington provides professional, affordable makeup applications and esthetician services in a beautifully designed and fun atmosphere. Artists are available seven days a week, in store or on the go, anywhere, anytime.

            p #{link_to "Visit Blushington", "https://www.blushington.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}

        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
          .ContentCopy__partner
            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-pinch-provisions.png", alt: "Pinch Provisions"

            p Pinch Provisions is the leading maker of personal care kits and premium emergency essentials, combining the sensibility of a fashion brand with the function of a modern general store.

            p #{link_to "Visit Pinch Provisions", "https://www.pinchprovisions.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}

        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
          .ContentCopy__partner
            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-white-elephant-designs.png", alt: "White Elephant Designs"

            p White Elephant Designs was founded by sisters Emily and Hope Winchell, on the premise that a personal touch makes otherwise simple gifts and decorations extraordinary. Today, they are a leading online destination for unique gifts, including home décor, gifts for all ages, jewelry, clothing and much more.

            p #{link_to "Visit White Elephant Designs", "https://thewhiteelephantdesigns.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}

      .row
        .col-md-4.col-xs-12
          .ContentCopy__partner
            = image_tag "landingpages/wedding-sweepstakes/logo-buff.png", alt: "The Buff"

            p The Buff believes there’s no such thing as one-size-fits-all when it comes to effective skincare. They tailor blends to your exact needs–and put your initials on the bottle. They get you, and they get your skin.

            p #{link_to "Visit The Buff", "https://www.itsthebuff.com", target: "_blank", class: "ContentCopy__link link-underline"}


